(152, 'Can Do vs. Can&#039;t Do Cultures', 'http://www.bhorowitz.com/can_do_vs_cant_do_cultures', 'img/3.jpg', 'Some people would like to turn the technology startup world into one great big company with a degenerative Can&#039;t Do Culture.', 'BenHorowitz BensBlog Startups', 'text', 'startups', 0),
(153, 'Cash Flow and Destiny', 'http://www.bhorowitz.com/cash_flow_and_destiny', 'img/3.jpg', 'If you are an entrepreneur, you have probably heard some crusty old CEO or investor say something like:cash is king.', 'BenHorowitz BensBlog Startups', 'text', 'startups', 0),
(154, 'Revenge of the Fat Guy', 'http://www.bhorowitz.com/revenge_of_the_fat_guy', 'img/3.jpg', 'Entrepreneurs should build the product that everybody wants before raising a boatload of cash to build the company.', 'BenHorowitz BensBlog Startups', 'text', 'startups', 0),
(155, 'How to overcome the startup growth plateau', 'http://insideintercom.io/how-to-overcome-the-startup-growth-plateau/', 'http://insideintercom.io/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Cloudsponge-chart_740-1.jpg', 'Jay Gibb, founder of CloudSponge, explains how he used highly-targeted emails to nurture relationships with new and existing customers.', 'InsideIntercom Startups Growth', 'text', 'startups', 0),
(156, 'Defining Static Web Apps', 'http://www.staticapps.org/articles/defining-static-web-apps', 'img/3.jpg', 'A Static Web Application is any web application that can be delivered directly to an end user''s browser without any server-side alteration of the HTML, CSS', 'Tech Web Dev Static Apps', 'text', 'tech', 0),
(157, 'Why Build Static Web Apps?', 'http://www.staticapps.org/articles/why-build-static-apps', 'img/3.jpg', 'Rather than assemble content in server-side processes, static web applications rely on the user''s browser to drive interaction and content rendering.', 'Tech Web Dev Static Apps', 'text', 'tech', 0),
(158, 'Thinking With Services for Static Web Apps', 'http://www.staticapps.org/articles/thinking-with-services', 'img/3.jpg', 'Building an application with service orientation comes with three key benefits.', 'Tech Dev Static Apps', 'text', 'tech', 0),
(159, 'Assembling Your Static App Stack', 'http://www.staticapps.org/articles/assembling-your-static-app-stack', 'img/3.jpg', 'Once you&#039ve decided to build a static web application, there are still several important choices to be made in terms of your app&#039;s tech stack.', 'Tech Web Dev Static Apps', 'text', 'tech', 0),
(160, 'Routing URLs in Static Web Apps', 'http://www.staticapps.org/articles/routing-urls-in-static-apps', 'img/3.jpg', 'So how can we maintain clean, readable URLs while still doing the heavy lifting in the browser?', 'Tech Web Dev Static Apps', 'text', 'tech', 0),
(161, 'Authentication and Authorization', 'http://www.staticapps.org/articles/authentication-and-authorization', 'img/3.jpg', 'Authentication is perhaps the single most common requirement of any application.', 'Tech Web Dev Static Apps', 'text', 'tech', 0),
(162, 'Cross-Domain Requests with CORS', 'http://www.staticapps.org/articles/cross-domain-requests-with-cors', 'img/3.jpg', 'Cross-Origin Resource Sharing CORS is a powerful technology for static web apps.', 'Tech Web Dev Static Apps', 'text', 'tech', 0),
(163, 'Front&dash;End Error Handling', 'http://www.staticapps.org/articles/front-end-error-handling', 'img/3.jpg', 'Error handling is a vital part of any app&#039;s user experience, and if done well, can leave your users feeling informed and properly considered.', 'Tech Web Dev Static Apps', 'text', 'tech', 0),
